Machines.name: NS-015
Machines.category: Paper Cup Machine, All Products
papercup

The NS-015 is a high-performance paper cup machine designed for efficient production in medium to large scale enterprises. It combines reliability with speed, capable of producing up to 100 cups per minute.
Voltage: 220V, Power: 1500W
Ideal for producing paper cups of various sizes, from 6oz to 16oz, suitable for hot and cold beverages.
Machines.description: This machine features a robust stainless steel construction that ensures durability and hygiene standards are met. It includes PLC control for precise operation and minimal wastage.
Machines.technical_specification: Material: Stainless steel, Weight: 500kg
Machines.optional_add_ons: Custom cup size molds available upon request.
Machines.faqs: Q: What is the warranty period? A: 1-year warranty provided for parts and service.

Machines.category: Paper Cup Machine, All Products
papercup
The NS-016 paper cup machine is designed for versatility and efficiency, catering to small to medium-scale enterprises. It offers reliable performance and ease of operation.
Voltage: 220V, Power: 1500W
Suitable for producing a variety of paper cup sizes, ranging from 4oz to 12oz, for both hot and cold beverages.
Machines.description: This machine is crafted from lightweight aluminum alloy, making it easy to transport and install. It features a user-friendly interface and low maintenance requirements.
Machines.technical_specification: Material: Aluminum alloy, Weight: 450kg
Machines.optional_add_ons: Automatic cup stacking unit available as an optional accessory.
Machines.faqs: Q: How many cups can it produce per minute? A: This machine can produce up to 80 cups per minute.

Machines.category: Paper Cup Machine, All Products
papercup
The NS-017 paper cup machine is known for its precision and high-speed production capabilities, suitable for large-scale operations requiring consistent quality.
Voltage: 220V, Power: 1800W
Designed to produce paper cups with sizes ranging from 8oz to 20oz, catering to a wide range of beverage serving needs.
Machines.description: Built with durable components and advanced PLC control, this machine ensures minimal downtime and optimal output. It includes features for custom mold adjustments and easy maintenance.
Machines.technical_specification: Material: Stainless steel, Weight: 600kg
Machines.optional_add_ons: Additional molds for special cup designs available upon request.
Machines.faqs: Q: What material can this machine handle? A: It is capable of handling both single and double PE coated paper.

paperlid
The Paper Flexo Machine is designed for printing on various paper surfaces, offering high-quality print results and flexibility.
Voltage: 220V, Power: 2000W
Ideal for printing logos, designs, and labels on paper cups, bowls, and plates.
Machines.description: This paper container machine or paper bowl making machine from Nessco is designed with high level of accuracy and international standards. This machine makes paper containers and bowls for food packaging and serving. The machines runs a whole procedure of paper feeding, bowl-fan wall sealing, oil lubrication, bottom punching, heating, rolling, rimming, rounding, and discharge as well.
Machines.technical_specification: Material: Aluminum alloy, Weight: 800kg
Machines.optional_add_ons: Additional color printing units available for multi-color designs.
Machines.faqs: Q: What is the printing speed of this machine? A: It can print up to 150 meters per minute.
Machines.related_product: Paper Flexo Machine 2, Paper Flexo Machine 3
